== Style Properties

--- indicator-size: Integer (Read)

    Size of check or radio indicator.
    * Allowed values: >= 0
    * Default value: 13

--- indicator-spacing: Integer (Read)

    Spacing around check or radio indicator.
    * Allowed values: >= 0
    * Default value: 2

== See Also

* Gtk::CheckMenuItem - add check buttons to your menus.
* Gtk::Button - a more general button.
* Gtk::ToggleButton - Gtk::CheckButton's parent.
* Gtk::RadioButton - group check buttons together.

